{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "熱灼夢", "storyInfo": "葦草祛除了深池士兵身上的法術後，得救的塞爾蒙與她談起了自己對深池寄託的理想。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你害怕我的火嗎？可你的火與我的是一樣的，拉芙希妮。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它會永遠燃燒，想要去矇住它的光焰，讓它熄滅，是徒勞的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不用畏懼讓人看到。為什麼不讓看到的人畏懼它呢？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道我的體內有一團火。只要去摸索就會感到灼痛，時間久了，痛覺甚至比我的想法先一步浮現。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父母告誡我們，把這天生的火焰吞下去，藏起來，不要被任何人看見。"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我知道，姐姐總是悄悄地燒掉自己不想要的東西，然後就能得到更好的。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不是也可以？"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸，可以帶我去書店嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天早上，我想試著扮演她，用她的語氣跟父母講話。"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一次她向父母提出要求的時候，父母都會像被火燙到一樣，驚惶又憐愛地答應。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和她有著一樣的相貌與聲音，穿著一樣的衣服，為什麼我不能假裝成她的樣子？"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想看蒸汽騎士冒險故事的續集......因為，我不想被其他人問，為什麼會有維多利亞人不喜歡看蒸汽騎士的故事。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......明天吧，拉芙希妮。爸爸媽媽今天已經很累了。", "name": "父親"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸......認出來我了？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我怎麼會分不清自己的兩個女兒呢？", "name": "父親"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個雪夜過後我才明白，他們不答應我，是因為我想要的東西太小了。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是她的話，是不會連一本新印的小說都要從父母那裡求來的。"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G6_decisivebattlealley_n", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bigbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bigbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bigbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟在她身後，拼命地奔跑。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "團聚的鐘聲響了，可是，家已經回不去了。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐......我們，要去哪裡？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你想去哪裡呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，不知道......", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然哪裡都不是家，那就隨便敲開一扇門吧。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只需要坦誠地告訴來開門的人，我們在這個節日的雪夜裡無家可歸。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論多麼冷漠的人，應該也是能對兩個孩子生出同情心的。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，拉芙希妮，別害怕。我在看著你呢。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在冰冷的紫色火焰映照下，我顫抖著敲開了第一扇門。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是剛剛取走了我們仇人性命的火焰，我卻好像知道，如果我做錯了什麼，它也會轉頭來殺死我。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1#2", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——可是，老師他做錯了什麼？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，塔拉人的街區在上演一齣戲劇，所以這樣的大雪夜裡，老師遲遲沒有回家。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐領我在老師的書房裡坐下。她沒有直接回答我的問題，只是溫和地注視著我。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，她對我很失望。我應該能夠自己找到答案。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他教我們，毀去無辜者的生活，激化塔拉人與維多利亞人的矛盾。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還......謀害了落魄的政敵，就像，那些維多利亞人，害死我們的父母一樣。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，取走他的性命......是該做的事情。", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐總是能做出正確的事情，我卻做不到。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她把槍送給了我，可每一次握住那柄燃燒著火焰的長槍，我都在發抖。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像此時。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說的......對嗎？", "name": "拉芙希妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，拉芙希妮。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡只不過會引他去往自己的理想。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i04", "xFrom": 100.0, "y": 100.0, "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yTo": 0.0, "duration": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i04", "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 100.0, "xTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 0.85, "yScaleTo": 0.85, "duration": 27.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm", "volume": 0.1}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 10.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他用陰謀與權術澆灌我們，剝下我們的自由與尊嚴，這當然可恨，但也只是可恨。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是他的手段業已精熟，他的野心卻太過狹隘，這才真正叫人惋惜。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想要的，不過是掌控一個易碎的空想國度，令我們做他戴冠的傀儡。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要握在手裡的權力，卻比他那狂人的空想，還要龐大得多。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你呢，拉芙希妮？你想要什麼呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的血脈與教養讓你高尚，這是好事，可你要是一無所求，我又該在身邊留什麼樣的位置給你呢？", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，這可是雪夜裡的願望......多麼大的野心，我都允許。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉芙希妮"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有回答。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只有小小的夢想，像壁爐裡一團溫暖的火。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不敢回答。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，我的妹妹。既然你不知道自己的欲望在何處，那就先成為我吧。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "往後，你與我便都是“領袖”。", "name": "愛布拉娜"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那火焰注視著我，我成為了她的影子。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wild_a", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......你一直跟著我？什麼時候？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，只是我從維恩那裡聽說，你在深池的死者隊伍裡，見到了自己的哥哥......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜你會自己來這裡。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事應該和你沒關係。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這一路......都在尋找這些被法術操縱的死者。我希望他們獲得平靜。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也的確能做到。就像剛才你看到的那樣。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不再有士兵行軍的腳步聲，荒野變得沉默。"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們誰也沒說話。過了一會，塞爾蒙蹲下來，拍了拍面罩上的塵土，然後小心地蓋在士兵的臉上。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那個多事的維恩，有沒有跟你說過我第一次見到深池時的事情？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時我們在城裡，我跟我哥，心情好就去排隊看看有沒有酒館需要臨時侍應生，心情不好就用彈弓打維多利亞人的窗玻璃。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，其實我也不知道那些貴族是不是維多利亞人，我只知道把我們從農用地塊上趕走的那個貴族是。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後有一天，有個受傷倒在小巷子裡的人用塔拉語叫住我，讓我幫她送信。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們猜到了她的身份。我送了信，還給她找了個地方藏起來。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我告訴她，在我心中這座城市最壞的維多利亞人，第一名要數那個頒佈法令的小鬍子貴族。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼針對塔拉酒鬼的酒稅啦，源石製品稅啦，把沒工作的塔拉人集中起來安置的法令啦，都是他在電視上說的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後還有駐紮在矮街的軍官，我眼睜睜看著他打死好幾個人，只要多瞪他一眼，就會被他抓走。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們鬼魂部隊要找襲擊目標，必須把這些人算上。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可她回答我，不對，深池的目標不是替塔拉人報復維多利亞人。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我哥就告訴她，哪個貴族有最大的房子，哪個貴族的宴會最氣派，哪個貴族的一間儲物室就能武裝一支部隊，養活一個地塊的農民。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說，那就更不對了，深池也不是要搶劫維多利亞人來救濟塔拉人。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還說，只是殺死一些人，然後自己坐上他們的位置，不會讓塔拉人的境況變得更好，只會把我們變成他們。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像學習維多利亞的禮儀，模仿維多利亞人的口音，這樣的塔拉人，也可以當上維多利亞的貴族......", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那，深池想要什麼，她告訴你們了嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，沒有。但後來我哥想明白了，所以我們決定加入深池，按照他們留下的訊息去找他們。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#2$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們離開了移動城市，前往鄰近的聚落。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在那條公路上，我突然想起來深池是怎麼清理目擊者的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很害怕，怕到不得不逃跑了。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不是恨每一個維多利亞人啊，我不恨的那些人，我還沒準備好讓他們流血啊。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但......那是不得不做的事。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，不喜歡這麼說。可是，深池是一支軍隊，軍隊面前只有戰爭。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，我當然知道。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理智上，我知道他們是正確的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "錯在我做不到。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......為什麼哥能做到的事我做不到？為什麼他能那麼堅定，我卻要逃跑？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼他能忍受死亡，忍受死後仍在燃燒，我卻連看著他變成這副模樣都不能忍受？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為什麼她能從灰燼裡站起來，我卻只能躲在影子裡哭泣？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "拉芙希妮，你想要的是什麼？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“我為你寫下，我生命所知的愛與夢”......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“可在那燃燒的狂喜裡，愛與夢都無處容身”......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......不會在念詩吧？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的？對我念詩？想顯得自己有教養？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#6$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉......我，不知道該怎麼說。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鼓勵別人、安慰別人的話，我可以講很多......但那都不是我的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......別念下去了......", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞爾蒙將臉埋在了雙手之間。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的悲痛與那些不再言語的深池士兵一樣，籠罩在深綠色的輪廓下。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我夢見......”他們低聲說。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好幾年前，我們還在維多利亞人的莊園裡工作的時候。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一天，我哥勸我扔掉手裡的事情，跟他一起溜出去玩。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們走了好長時間，走到了農用地塊的邊緣，望著下面的荒野。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看不到盡頭的土地，土地上開滿野花。我哥說，那就是塔拉。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說了很多又蠢又自大的話，很大聲地對著風唱歌。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說維多利亞人奪走了我們的語言，所以我們有很多話想說卻說不出，只能把愛和悲傷都藏在古老的民謠裡。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還說我們做了一件了不起的事，我們今天不給維多利亞人幹活，這就是反抗了維多利亞人。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#2$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時他可能真的很自豪，真的夢想著成為傳說故事裡的英雄......哈。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#2$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也一樣。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你留給他的火焰，很漂亮。就像那天我們看到的花。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可它不是真的花，只是......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“從我們的生到死，不過是眨眼一瞬。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......甚至，你都沒辦法握住它。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，我不在乎。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "塞爾蒙", "content": "我早就知道他會死。我們去找深池的時候，連我都做好了自己會死的準備。"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "塞爾蒙", "end": "true", "content": "我......不在乎。", "joined": "我早就知道他會死。我們去找深池的時候，連我都做好了自己會死的準備。我......不在乎。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也從來不信他能像自己吹噓的一樣，像我們的夢想一樣，死得像個英雄。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，葦草......我想要聽句實話，你自己的實話。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他到死還在追求的東西，那個......深池許諾的未來，是假的嗎？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#5$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firestorm", "volume": 0.1}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑夜下，一簇火焰從槍尖燃起。"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在火光的映照中，葦草看見，淚水終於流過她的臉龐。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}